        "description": "<note> <p>This documentation is for version 1 of the Amazon Kinesis Data Analytics API, which only supports SQL applications. Version 2 of the API supports SQL and Java applications. For more information about version 2, see <a href=\"/kinesisanalytics/latest/apiv2/Welcome.html\">Amazon Kinesis Data Analytics API V2 Documentation</a>.</p> </note> <p>Adds a CloudWatch log stream to monitor application configuration errors. For more information about using CloudWatch log streams with Amazon Kinesis Analytics applications, see <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/kinesisanalytics/latest/dev/cloudwatch-logs.html\">Working with Amazon CloudWatch Logs</a>.</p>",
